<section class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Syntactically Sugary Development</div>
  <div class="accent-bar"></div>
  <h1>Where Technology Meets<br /><span>Business</span> Meets Language</h1>
  <p class="subhead">The art of refining the complex into the intuitive.</p>
  <p class="body-copy">
    I'm <strong>James Huschle</strong> — 25 years of Fortune 500 technology leadership,
    now applied to cloud architecture, machine learning, and AI-native systems.
    I've managed engineering teams, built greenfield platforms, and delivered on roadmaps
    that crossed departments, continents, and budget cycles. The rarest thing in technology
    consulting isn't technical skill — it's someone who can translate fluently between
    the engineering team and the people writing the checks.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a class="btn-primary" href="#work">See My Work</a>
    <a class="btn-secondary" href="#contact">Let's Talk</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 4rem 5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .accent-bar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent-dark);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 span { color: var(--accent); }

  .subhead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .body-copy {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .body-copy strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--accent-dark);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #1d4ed8; }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
